 to visit if you wish to know about India\'s profile, its unique culture &amp; heritage, National Identity Symbols, States/UTs/Districts. There is also a special section exclusively for the Kids !!</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Sectors</a></h1><p>Useful information and links about the various sectors of the Indian Economy, such as Agriculture, Industry, HRD, Health, Communications &amp; IT, Finance &amp; Banking, Rural Development and more...</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">How do I?</a></h1><p>Quick links to a variety of online citizen services across sectors being provided by the Government... right from obtaining a birth certificate to applying for a Passport.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Directories</a></h1><p>Access the Indian Government web directory, locate a telephone number in any State/UT of India, find out an STD/PIN Code of any region in the Country or know about the NGOs operating in the Country.</p><p>A section featuring various geographical and thematic maps of India.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Documents</a></h1><p>A collection of links to important documents and study reports published or issued by the Indian Government. Review date is captured internally as valid up to field. Content is reviewed and archived as per the Content Review Policy (CRP) and Content Archival Policy (CAP) given in the Portal.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Tenders</a></h1><p>View the Tenders floated by the various ministries/departments of the Indian Government at the Central/State level for outsourcing different works and contracts.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Forms</a></h1><p>A repository of important Application Forms required for availing various services and facilities provided by the Government. Easy search facility to locate the desired forms.</p></div><div><h1>India-Greetings</h1><p>Send personalised greetings featuring photographs on the myriad, colourful aspects of India to your loved ones.</p></div><div><h1>Opinion Poll</h1><p>Cast your vote in the opinion poll question based on some topic of National interest or an issue that concerns our daily lives as Indians.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Spotlight</a></h1><p>A section highlighting an issue or a topic which is much in news and would be of interest to any well informed Indian citizen.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">News</a></h1><p>Read the daily headlines and detailed National/International news.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Speak Out-Your Opinion</a></h1><p>Please spare some time and take this online survey to let us know your feedback on this portal and your suggestions on how we can improve it further.</p></div><div><h1>Sign India</h1><p>Register with us and let us know about yourself and your area of interest to receive e-mail alerts about latest updates on different sections of this Portal.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Site Map</a></h1><p>A index based representation of the contents on this Portal. It is organised hierarchically, breaking down the Portal\'s information into increasingly specific subject areas.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Search</a></h1><p>Search through the contents of this Portal by giving appropriate key-words.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Terms of Use</a></h1><p>Read our Disclaimer, Privacy policy and Linking Policy.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Suggest this Page to a Friend</a></h1><p>An easy option to email a link to a page on this Portal that you find worth recommending to your friends.</p></div><div><h1><a href=\"#\">About the Portal</a></h1><p>A brief background on the development of this Portal with an insight on its inherent objectives.</p></div></div><div style=\"clear: both;\"></div></div>','<div class=\"portal-sections\"><div class=\"help-content-left-panel help-content-panel\"><div><h1><a href=\"#\">Citizens</a></h1><p>Useful information and links for Indian Citizens residing within the Country on topics such as Health, Education, Employment, Housing, Travel &amp; Tourism, Banking &amp; Insurance and Ta